SELECT
  avg(ava_debt)  as 'debt'
FROM HourlyJourney
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(start) and ava_debt > 0

SELECT
  avg(exp_debt)  as 'debt'
FROM HourlyJourney
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(start) and exp_debt > 0

SELECT
  avg(lat_debt)  as 'debt'
FROM HourlyJourney
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(start) and lat_debt > 0

SELECT 1 as 'debt'
FROM HourlyJourney
WHERE $__timeFilter(start) 
group by journey
having sum(ava_debt) > 0

SELECT 1 as 'no debt'
FROM HourlyJourney
WHERE $__timeFilter(start) 
group by journey
having sum(ava_debt) = 0

SELECT 1 as 'debt'
FROM HourlyJourney
WHERE $__timeFilter(start) 
group by journey
having sum(exp_debt) > 0

SELECT 1 as 'no debt'
FROM HourlyJourney
WHERE $__timeFilter(start) 
group by journey
having sum(exp_debt) = 0

SELECT 1 as 'debt'
FROM HourlyJourney
WHERE $__timeFilter(start) 
group by journey
having sum(lat_debt) > 0

SELECT 1 as 'no debt'
FROM HourlyJourney
WHERE $__timeFilter(start) 
group by journey
having sum(lat_debt) = 0

SELECT
  journey, 
  avg(ava_debt) as 'debt'
FROM HourlyJourney
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(start) and ava_debt > 0 
group by journey
order by debt desc
limit 5

SELECT
  journey, 
  avg(exp_debt) as 'debt'
FROM HourlyJourney
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(start) and exp_debt > 0 
group by journey
order by debt desc
limit 5

SELECT
  journey, 
  avg(lat_debt) as 'debt'
FROM HourlyJourney

SELECT
  start AS "time",
  avg(nullif(ava_debt, 0)) as 'availability debt'
FROM HourlyJourney
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(start) 
group by start
order by  'availability debt'

SELECT
  start AS "time",
  avg(nullif(exp_debt, 0)) as 'experience debt'
FROM HourlyJourney
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(start) 
group by start

SELECT
  start AS "time",
  avg(nullif(lat_debt,0)) as 'latency debt'
FROM HourlyJourney
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(start) 
group by start
ORDER BY start

SELECT  journey, 
        max(avaSlo) as 'ava slo',
        ifnull(AVG(NULLIF(ava_debt ,0)),0) as 'ava debt',
        max(expSlo) as 'exp slo',
        ifnull(AVG(NULLIF(exp_debt ,0)),0) as 'exp debt',
        max(latSlo) as 'lat slo',
        ifnull(AVG(NULLIF(lat_debt ,0)),0) as 'lat debt'
FROM HourlyJourney
WHERE
$__timeFilter(start) 
Group by journey

SELECT journey, email
FROM  Journeys J 
join JourneyLeaders JL on J.id = JL.journeyId 
join Members M on JL.memberId = M.id
